		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Wizard of Oz experiment</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>In the field of <a href="/wiki/Human-computer_interaction" title="Human-computer interaction">human-computer interaction</a>, a <b>Wizard of Oz experiment</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Research" title="Research">research</a> experiment in which subjects interact with a <a href="/wiki/Computer" title="Computer">computer</a> system that subjects believe to be autonomous, but which is actually being operated or partially operated by an unseen <a href="/wiki/Human_being" title="Human being" class="mw-redirect">human being</a>.</p>
